{"tid":829069,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"歐盟再以壟斷法查美企 這次主角是Amazon","createTime":"2018-09-20T06:49:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-21T05:31:09.000Z","uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"1e0beb72b4162158f0dc3bbb6306b1cee01695e7","tid":829069,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T06:49:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180920/large/1537414941_a98b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180920%2Flarge%2F1537414941_a98b.jpg&h=8d2d8dc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歐盟競爭事務專員Margrethe Vestager曾向Google發出50億美元天價罰單，現時她的新調查目標是亞馬遜。(資料圖片)<br />\n科企巨人殺手、歐盟競爭事務專員Margrethe Vestager週三表示，歐盟已展開對亞馬遜﹙Amazon﹚潛在反壟斷行為的初步調查。<br />\n<br />\nVestager關注到亞馬遜如何使用來自第三方賣家的數據，以幫助自己預測「new big thing」。她解釋，亞馬遜作為網購平台收集的銷售數據固然合法，用來幫助小商家產品賣得更好亦是沒有問題，但是假如亞馬遜利用這些數據，作為自行運算預測新趨勢、用戶偏好、消費者行為等等，這便有機會構成潛在的違法行為。<br />\n<br />\n她指目前還不是一個正式的調查，歐盟已收集有關資料作進一步分析，包括向亞馬遜第三方賣家收集調查問卷，暫時尚未得出任何結論。<br />\n<br />\n亞馬遜平台上的第三方賣家，是企業主要收入來源之一，2018年第二季度達97億美元，同比增長40％，亞馬遜暫時未對事件作任何回應。<br />\n<br />\nVestager今年7月曾向Google發出50億美元的天價罰款，理由是手機系統Android涉及壟斷行為；而她亦正在處理Apple手機差電案，涉嫌壟斷行為。2016年歐盟已勒令Apple向愛爾蘭繳付160億美元稅款，而Apple才剛付清款項。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180920/58702592\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180920%2F58702592&d=kThX8bkn0l1ex4g4vi8cw%2BargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=b2d2dfe2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180920%2F58702592&h=8b8e24e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180920/58702592</a>"},{"pid":"dcc2f70f50b9ddba256d063fc9b96272b5758ad1","tid":829069,"uid":13303,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T06:55:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 掠完英國掠美國"},{"pid":"17c47664ec16689f8c1db12c032e9e860be8de75","tid":829069,"uid":39200,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T07:01:36.000Z","msg":"等睇 Trump 另類反撃<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a7912f1f3ba1e5afec361298816fb818b8ffb38","tid":829069,"uid":32938,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T07:04:30.000Z","msg":"又收保護費"},{"pid":"7433b53bc898093965c34f4e220f8277bb5db483","tid":829069,"uid":26770,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T07:12:37.000Z","msg":"港豬真係好笑<br />\n<br />\n如果反壟斷法係100%差<br />\n現在就係有反壟斷法避免一台獨大<br />\n好多跨國大企有能力夾死班細企就係因為怕反壟斷法無做<br />\n<br />\n如果歐盟100%錯, 歐盟的反傾銷又要盲反?<br />\n歐盟反傾銷法頭號針對國家係中共"},{"pid":"df13417c89aec76175553ce9d85d6684078b052f","tid":829069,"uid":39470,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"17c47664ec16689f8c1db12c032e9e860be8de75","tid":829069,"uid":39200,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T07:01:36.000Z","msg":"等睇 Trump 另類反撃<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T07:42:11.000Z","msg":"Trump自己都成日屌鳩Amazon啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25d6fbf740225557d4e1984e6266477d329057de","tid":829069,"uid":17103,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T07:45:17.000Z","msg":"因為你班垃圾 eu 家下好多網站都要 click 個 &quot;Accept / Okay&quot; 好撚煩"},{"pid":"f4164577152f08a483c3bf64dd93318344dbd5e7","tid":829069,"uid":90704,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T07:54:37.000Z","msg":"反壟斷？<br />\n壟斷先好呀<br />\n啲嘢越壟斷越平㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f7599b7f45535c79bd7b63389a683b156e83a58","tid":829069,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25d6fbf740225557d4e1984e6266477d329057de","tid":829069,"uid":17103,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":